<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="study-v">study <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'stʌdi/    美 /'stʌdi/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>学习；攻读：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I would like to live to study, and not study to live.
我愿意为了学习而活着，不愿意为了活着而学习。</p><footer>——培根</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>研究；调查：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Scientists are studying the photographs of Mars for signs of life.
科学家们正在研究火星照片，看有没有生命的迹象。</p></div></div>